{"tid":1392272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要只說「罷工」試著說「請一日假」或「在家工作」","createTime":"2019-07-31T16:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:48:45.000Z","uid":268801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e01ebd9df2104cd33b67d29f795c37de86879ee0","tid":1392272,"uid":268801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"其實好多香港人都想支持三罷<br />\n不過慣左做港豬 唔係個個咁容易突破到心理關口<br />\n此終 罷工依個名字 唔係人人咁快就接受到<br />\n咁不如係文宣上<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要只說「罷工」<br />\n試著說「請一日假」或「在家工作」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea1eeb5ac313ca6e7c6909033542a2c0ace6a307","tid":1392272,"uid":268801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0900707b1b1afbc3ed2188a7b99a2b9ef7f2114f","tid":1392272,"uid":268801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6e5c8e794c40b0af4502f5ff40d0d3c74d70c8a","tid":1392272,"uid":268801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c0a386e20a3bee244d68188ad4430572a323318","tid":1392272,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"唔支持<br />\n罷工係一個姿態嚟<br />\n真係想啲人出於自發想用罷工嘅手段<br />\n無謂依啲位美化佢<br />\n希望啲人喺思維上都會知道今次香港嘅問題係非同小可，真係要認真罷工嚟對待"}]}